{"tid":1284632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對方咁高調使用指模、DNA 鑑證, 其實想引起恐慌。","createTime":"2019-07-04T08:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T11:06:42.000Z","uid":67412,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"569bec7f022208eeeee6787a04b0a537fc5a9fc3","tid":1284632,"uid":67412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T08:55:46.000Z","msg":"來自yahoo<br />\n<br />\n代朋友post<br />\n<br />\n- 對方咁高調使用指模、DNA 鑑證, 其實想引起恐慌。<br />\n- 警察可能冇咗當日証據,  所以依家先咁高調要依賴科學鑑證嘅方法。<br />\n- 冇證人, 冇錄影, 單憑科學鑑證入罪其實有難度。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E8%AD%A6%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%90%9C%E8%AD%89-%E7%A7%98%E6%9B%B8%E8%99%95%E9%81%BA%E5%A4%B1%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%A1%AC%E4%BB%B6-015800823.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2590%259C%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E7%25A7%2598%25E6%259B%25B8%25E8%2599%2595%25E9%2581%25BA%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E7%25A1%25AC%25E4%25BB%25B6-015800823.html&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI6d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=28c6ea67\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E8%AD%A6%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%90%9C%E8%AD%89-%E7%A7%98%E6%9B%B8%E8%99%95%E9%81%BA%E5%A4%B1%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%A1%AC%E4%BB%B6-015800823.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我哋依家仲係行緊普通法, 疑點利益歸於被告。<br />\n都係嗰一句, 『阿sir我冇嘢講, 你夠料就charge我。』<br />\n唔俾口供, 就已經安全好多。<br />\n<br />\n做好briefing, 教大家被捕之後應該點做, 如果唔係小朋友驚起嚟就爆曬, 又或者俾人氹多兩氹, 就乜都會講。<br />\n有冇人可以做啲片, 放喺網度 ? 教大家, 警察會用啲乜污糟那渣嘅方法, 要你講嘢。"},{"pid":"59b984c715f4c455db7ee94d573354a442374df6","tid":1284632,"uid":79445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:03:13.000Z","msg":"Good<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b24ffb490d703bd8e59218c64fea1230235ea9","tid":1284632,"uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T09:03:50.00